title: Lilie James’ Parents Call For Education Into Coercive Behaviours Following Brutal Murder | 10 News
description: Lilie James' parents have issued a heartfelt plea that someone who commits murder is never a good bloke. Her recommendations will now go to the Premier's department for urgent action to protect women's lives. title: Hoodoo Gurus Superfan’s Wish Comes True After 40 Years | 10 News+
description: Few people would hold out hope of receiving of a reply to a handwritten letter from a famous rockstar 40 years after posting it. But patience has paid off for a Melbourne megafan of Aussie rock gods, The Hoodoo Gurus. Back in 1985 the band had just released a second hit album and superfan Elisse Baitz, who was just 13 years old at the time, decided to send her idols a letter. That letter has just been answered by none other than band's frontman, Dave Faulkner.
